{"title_page": "Norio Tsukudani", "text_new": "{{Nihongo|'''Norio Tsukudani'''|\u4f43\u716e \u306e\u308a\u304a|Tsukudani Norio|born on April 16 1993, in [[Nagaoka, Niigata]]}} is a Japanese female [[mangaka|manga artist]] and [[illustrator]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.toranoana.jp/torabook/toradayo/2013_05/sp03/|script-title=ja:\u4f43\u716e\u306e\u308a\u304a\u5148\u751f\u30a4\u30f3\u30bf\u30d3\u30e5\u30fc|trans-title=Interview with Norio Tsukudani|publisher=[[Comic Toranoana]]|accessdate=March 9, 2014|language=Japanese}}</ref> Her work ''[[Himegoto]]'' has been adapted into an [[anime]] which began airing in Japan in July 2014.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2014-02-24/tsukudani-cross-dressing-4-panel-manga-himegoto-gets-anime|title=Tsukudani's Cross-Dressing 4-Panel Manga Himegoto Gets Anime|publisher=[[Anime News Network]]|date=February 24, 2014|accessdate=March 9, 2014}}</ref> She also took charge of the illustrations for ''[[Daitoshokan no Hitsujikai#Printed media|Daitoshokan no Hitsujikai: Hitoribotchi no Diva]]'', one of the manga adaptations for ''[[Daitoshokan no Hitsujikai]]'', an [[eroge|adult]] [[visual novel]] developed by [[August (company)|August]]. She hosts a [[d\u014djin|d\u014djin circle]] named {{Nihongo|\"armomo\"|\u3042\u3082\u3082|Amomo}}.\n\nShe also voiced one of her own characters in her anime Himegoto.\n\nShe also streams on [[YouTube]] as [[Virtual YouTuber]] ''Inuyama Tamaki''.\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* [http://armomo.blog20.fc2.com/index.php armomo] {{in lang|ja}}\n* {{Twitter}} {{in lang|ja}}\n* {{ann|people|127334}}\n* [https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC8NZiqKx6fsDT3AVcMiVFyA Youtube Channel] {{in lang|ja}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Tsukudani, Norio}}\n[[Category:Japanese illustrators]]\n[[Category:Manga artists from Niigata Prefecture]]\n[[Category:People from Nagaoka, Niigata]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:1993 births]]\n", "text_old": "{{Nihongo|'''Norio Tsukudani'''|\u4f43\u716e \u306e\u308a\u304a|Tsukudani Norio|born on April 16 1993, in [[Nagaoka, Niigata]]}} is a Japanese female [[mangaka|manga artist]] and [[illustrator]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.toranoana.jp/torabook/toradayo/2013_05/sp03/|script-title=ja:\u4f43\u716e\u306e\u308a\u304a\u5148\u751f\u30a4\u30f3\u30bf\u30d3\u30e5\u30fc|trans-title=Interview with Norio Tsukudani|publisher=[[Comic Toranoana]]|accessdate=March 9, 2014|language=Japanese}}</ref> Her work ''[[Himegoto]]'' has been adapted into an [[anime]] which began airing in Japan in July 2014.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2014-02-24/tsukudani-cross-dressing-4-panel-manga-himegoto-gets-anime|title=Tsukudani's Cross-Dressing 4-Panel Manga Himegoto Gets Anime|publisher=[[Anime News Network]]|date=February 24, 2014|accessdate=March 9, 2014}}</ref> She also took charge of the illustrations for ''[[Daitoshokan no Hitsujikai#Printed media|Daitoshokan no Hitsujikai: Hitoribotchi no Diva]]'', one of the manga adaptations for ''[[Daitoshokan no Hitsujikai]]'', an [[eroge|adult]] [[visual novel]] developed by [[August (company)|August]]. She hosts a [[d\u014djin|d\u014djin circle]] named {{Nihongo|\"armomo\"|\u3042\u3082\u3082|Amomo}}.\n\nShe also voiced one of her own characters in her anime Himegoto.\n\nShe also streams on [[YouTube]] as [[Virtual YouTuber]] ''Inuyama Tamaki''.\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* [http://armomo.blog20.fc2.com/index.php armomo] {{in lang|ja}}\n* {{Twitter}} {{in lang|ja}}\n* {{ann|people|127334}}\n* [https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC8NZiqKx6fsDT3AVcMiVFyA Inuyama Tamaki Channel]\n\n{{Authority control}}\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Tsukudani, Norio}}\n[[Category:Japanese illustrators]]\n[[Category:Manga artists from Niigata Prefecture]]\n[[Category:People from Nagaoka, Niigata]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:1993 births]]\n", "name_user": "MarkF99999", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eExternal links", "url_page":