zar|Grezar]] {{Goal|1}}<br />[[Valentino Mazzola|Mazzola]] {{Goal|30||57}}<br />[[Romeo Menti|Menti II]] {{Goal|31}}<br />[[Guglielmo Gabetto|Gabetto]] {{Goal|55}}\n|goals2 = {{Goal|14||19}} [[Giacomo Neri|Neri II]]\n|result=W\n}}\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|date = 6 April 1947\n|time = 15:30 [[UTC+1]]\n|round = 27\n|team1 = [[Bologna F.C.|Bologna]]\n|team2 = Torino\n|score = 1-1\n|report=http://calcio-seriea.net/tabellini/1946/3888/\n|location= [[Bologna]]\n|stadium = [[Stadio Renato Dall'Ara|Stadio Comunale]]\n|attendance = 46.000\n|referee = Guido Agnolin\n|goals1 = [[Ferruccio Valcareggi|Valcareggi]] {{Goal|4}}\n|goals2 = {{Goal|63}} [[Ezio Loik|Loik]]\n|result=D\n}}\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|date = 13 April 1947\n|time = 15:30 [[UTC+1]]\n|round= 28\n|team1 = [[Brescia Calcio|Brescia]]\n|team2 = Torino\n|score = 0-1\n|report=http://calcio-seriea.net/tabellini/1946/4008/\n|location = Brescia\n|stadium = [[Stadium di Viale Piave]]\n|attendance = 46 000\n|referee= Generoso Dattilo\n|goals1 = \n|goals2 = {{Goal|15}} [[Ezio Loik|Loik]]\n|result=W\n}}\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|date = 20 April 1947\n|time = 15:30 [[UTC+1]]\n|round = 29\n|team1 = Torino\n|team2 = [[Vicenza Calcio|Vicenza]]\n|score = 6-0\n|report=http://calcio-seriea.net/tabellini/1946/3770/\n|location = [[Torino]]\n|stadium = [[Stadio Filadelfia]]\n|attendance = \n|referee = Massironi\n|goals1 = [[Ezio Loik|Loik]] {{Goal|24}}<br />[[Valentino Mazzola|Mazzola]] {{Goal|29||31||30}}<br />[[Pietro Ferraris|Ferraris II]] {{Goal|57}}<br />[[Guglielmo Gabetto|Gabetto]] {{Goal|64}}\n|goals2 = \n|result=W\n}}\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|date = 4 May 1947\n|time = 16:00 [[UTC+1]]\n|round = 30\n|team1 = Livorno\n|team2 = Torino\n|score = 0-2\n|report=http://calcio-seriea.net/tabellini/1946/3908/\n|location = Livorno\n|stadium = [[Stadio Armando Picchi|Stadio Ardenza]]\n|attendance = 20 000\n|referee = Luigi Gemini\n|goals1 = \n|goals2 = {{Goal|10}} [[Eusebio Castigliano|Castigliano]]<br />{{Goal|79}} [[Gug